# NIFYA Frontend

This document describes the structure of the NIFYA frontend application.

## Key Files

- [package.json](mdc:frontend/package.json) - Frontend package dependencies and scripts
- [vite.config.ts](mdc:frontend/vite.config.ts) - Vite build configuration
- [index.html](mdc:frontend/index.html) - Main HTML entry point
- [tailwind.config.js](mdc:frontend/tailwind.config.js) - Tailwind CSS configuration

## Source Code

The frontend source code is organized in the [src](mdc:frontend/src/) directory:
- Components
- Pages
- Services
- Utils
- Styles

## Deployment

The frontend is deployed to Netlify at https://clever-kelpie-60c3a6.netlify.app.

The [Dockerfile](mdc:frontend/Dockerfile) and [cloudbuild.yaml](mdc:frontend/cloudbuild.yaml) define the build and deployment process.
